<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，  毛克利和麦苏雅住在她的小屋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们吃晚饭时，她告诉他自己丈夫已经死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，那天晚上你救了我们的命，毛克利。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛里充满了感激的泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在这里过得很好。附近有个村庄，我很满意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早上，毛克利准备走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定要再来！”麦苏雅轻声说，拥抱着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爱你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利觉得喉咙发紧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也爱你，麦苏雅。我很快就会回来。我保证。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他向沼泽地走去时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只大野兽从高高的草丛中跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴希拉！”毛克利惊讶地说，“你在这里做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我跟着你来的。”巴希拉回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你又跟着我了？”毛克利笑着摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总是跟着我。我的狼妈妈和格瑞布拉德也是这样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉看起来很不安。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要......你要回森林吗？”他问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我......我以为你会和那个女人待在一起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我不属于人类，巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那群人赶走了我，记得吗？就像狼群一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉盯着毛克利看了几秒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他抬起他的下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“摸摸我的下巴下面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利乖乖地把他的手指放在巴希拉的下巴下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹的毛覆盖着厚厚的肌肉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，毛克利摸了摸没有毛的部分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”他问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是项圈的痕迹。”巴希拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林里没有人知道这件事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也出生在人类中间，毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我住在王宫的一个笼子里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”毛克利惊讶地眨了眨眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉也和人类一起生活过？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是为什么你小时候我在岩石会议上为你说了话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉继续说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我母亲死在王宫的笼子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那之后，我在那里没有家人，而且......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利无法想象美丽、强壮的黑豹被关在笼子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“笼子一定感觉像监狱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是个监狱。”巴希拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我住在那里，从来没见过森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，有一天晚上，非常神奇，我发现了自己的力量。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我告诉自己我是一只黑豹，不是人们的玩物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一爪子就把那个锁头打碎了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利笑了。那才是巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你知道我的秘密了，小兄弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我回到了森林，我属于那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你也一样......”巴希拉停了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是一个人类。所以总有一天，你会回到属于你的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，对不起，巴希拉，但你错了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利坚定地摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我永远不会再和人类住在一起的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去看了麦苏雅。但仅此而已。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拍了拍黑豹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，等我长大独立了，我会回来看你和巴鲁。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一个穿着白色连衣裙的女孩儿出现在路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利和巴希拉躲到灌木丛后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当女孩儿经过的时候，毛克利用手拨开灌木丛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着那个女孩儿向沼泽地走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个男孩儿既是人又是狼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉边想边温柔地看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但总有一天，他会变得更像人，而不是狼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个女孩儿不见了，巴希拉用鼻子碰了一下毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你准备好回家了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”毛克利跳到黑豹背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们一起向森林深处跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>